attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX nas: <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#> SELECT ?engines WHERE {nas:ASA14 nas:numberOfEngines ?engines1 . nas:AAL20 nas:numberOfEngines ?engines2 . }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the combined number of engines for flights ASA14 and AAL20 by querying their respective numberOfEngines properties.
